dct_title_s: Bronx bus map : updated for Spring 1996 / MTA ; New York City Transit (Recto)
dct_description_sm: Includes text, index to points of interest, and color-coded bus-route directory. Panel title. Text, specimen map, extensive bus-route directory (time/frequency tables), and advertisement on verso. "22-30-1009. 5 4 3 2 1."
dct_publisher_sm: [New York] : New York City Transit Authority, 1996.
